Participate in an online cybersecurity discussion.

In this activity, I participated in an online cybersecurity discussion on a Discord server. The discussion was about SQL injection vulnerabilities and database security.

I observed how users discussed the risks of unsanitised inputs and how it can lead to bypassing authentication systems. There was also an example SQL query shown, which helped me understand how such vulnerabilities can affect real systems.

Through this discussion, I learned how developers and security enthusiasts share knowledge and analyse vulnerabilities in real-world applications.

This activity helped me better understand how cybersecurity issues are discussed in online communities and how important it is to handle user input securely.
